Step 1.	Start.
Step 2.	Accept sentence from the user.
Step 3.	If if the sentence does not end with a '.','!','?' Return invalid input and stop.
Step 4.	Using split() convert the sentence into array of words.
Step 5.	Sort words using bubble sort technique.
Step 6.	Verify whether the lengths of two words are equal.
Step 7. If step 6 is true then compare the value of both words using compared to and sort accordingly.
Step 8.	Print the words to give the final sorted array.
Step 9.	End.
